Module it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034

Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034.messages.setupPhase

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerCardsChoice
    Message from the client to the server that communicate the gods chosen by the most god like player.
    AnswerFirstPlayer
    Message from the client to the server that communicate the first player chosen.
    AnswerPersonalGod
    Message from the client to the server that communicate the personal god chosen by the sender.
    AnswerPlaceWorker
    Message from the client to the server that communicate the tile where the player wants to place his workers.
    FirstPlayerInfo
    Message from the server to the client that communicates which is the first player to start the current game.
    GodLikeInfo
    Message from the server to the client that communicates which is the most god like player.
    InfoIsPlacing
    Message from the server to the client that communicates which is the player starting to play in this turn.
    InitializeBoard
    Message from server to client initializing the board for the first time.
    ReceivedWorkerChoice
    Message sent from server to client asserting to have received the placing of a worker.
    RequestCardsChoice
    Message from the server to the client that requests to the player the choice of all the gods cards.
    RequestFirstPlayer
    Message from the server to the client that requests to the player the first player choice.
    RequestPersonalGod
    Message from the server to the client that requests to the player the personal god choice.
    RequestPlaceWorker
    Message from the server to the client that requests to the player the placing of a worker.
    SetupAnswer
    Answer from the client to the server, in response to a SetupRequest.
    SetupRequest
    Answer from the server to the client, during the setup phase of a game.
